	"system": {
		"description": "<p>As an action, you ignite a campfire you can see with a relaxing and calming firelight. While within 15ft of this campfire, creatures ignore extreme cold, and gain advantage on saving throws against fear. Allies who spend hit dice as part of a short rest while in the Sanctuary regain twice as many hit points.</p><p>The fire remains ignited in this way until you dismiss it or after 8 hours.</p>",
